quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  20,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  20,1,Taa-Haa
  20,2,Maaa anzalnaa 'alaikal Qur-aana litashqaaa
  20,3,Illaa tazkiratal limany yakshaa
  20,4,Tanzeelam mimman khalaqal arda was samaawaatil 'ulaa
  20,5,Ar-Rahmaanu 'alal 'Arshis tawaa
  20,6,Lahoo maa fis samaawaati wa maa fil ardi wa maa bainahumaa wa maa tahtassaraa
  20,7,Wa in tajhar bilqawli fainnahoo ya'lamus sirra wa akhfaa
  20,8,Allaahu laaa ilasha illaa Huwa lahul Asmaaa'ul Husnaa
  20,9,Wa hal ataaka hadeesu Moosa
  20,10,Iz ra aa naaran faqaala li alhlihim kusooo inneee aanastu naaral la'alleee aateekum minhaa biqabasin aw ajidu 'alan naari hudaa
  20,11,Falammaaa ataahaa noodiya yaa Moosaa
  20,12,Inneee Ana Rabbuka fakhla' na'laika innaka bilwaadil muqaddasi Tuwaa
  20,13,Wa anakhtartuka fastami' limaa yoohaa
  20,14,Innaneee Anal laahu laaa ilaaha illaa Ana fa'budnee wa aqimis-salaata lizikree
  20,15,Innas Saa'ata aatiyatun akaadu ukhfeehaa litujzaa kullu nafsim bimaa tas'aa
  20,16,Falaa yasuddannnaka 'anhaa mal laa yu'minu bihaa wattaba'a hawaahu fatardaa
  20,17,Wa maa tilka bi yamee nika yaa Moosaa
  20,18,Qaala hiya 'asaaya atawakka'u alaihaa wa ahushshu bihaa 'alaa ghanamee wa liya feehaa ma aaribu ukhraa
  20,19,Qaala alqihaa yaa Moosaa
  20,20,Fa-alqaahaa fa -izaa hiya haiyatun tas'aa
  20,21,Qaala khuzhaa wa laa ta khaf sanu'eeduhaa seeratahal oolaa
  20,22,Wadmum yadaka ilaa janaahika takhruj baidaaa'a min ghairi sooo'in Aayatan ukhraa
  20,23,Linuriyaka min Aayaatinal Kubra
  20,24,Izhab ilaa Fir'awna innahoo taghaa (section 1)
  20,25,Qaala Rabbish rah lee sadree
  20,26,Wa yassir leee amree
  20,27,Wahlul 'uqdatam milli saanee
  20,28,Yafqahoo qawlee
  20,29,Waj'al lee wazeeram min ahlee
  20,30,Haaroona akhee
  20,31,Ushdud biheee azree
  20,32,Wa ashrik hu feee amree
  20,33,Kai nusabbihaka kaseeraa
  20,34,Wa nazkuraka kaseeraa
  20,35,Innaka kunta binaa baseeraa
  20,36,Qaala qad ooteeta su'laka yaa Moosaa
  20,37,Wa laqad manannaa 'alaika marratan ukhraaa
  20,38,Iz awhainaaa ilaaa ummika maa yoohaaa
  20,39,Aniqzifeehi fit Taabooti faqzifeehi fil yammi fal yul qihil yammu bis saahili yaakhuzhu 'aduwwul lee wa 'aduwwul lah; wa alqaitu 'alaika mahabbatam minnee wa litusna'a 'alaa 'ainee
  20,40,Iz tamsheee ukhtuka fataqoolu hal adullukum 'alaa mai yakfuluhoo faraja 'naaka ilaaa ummika kai taqarra 'ainuhaa wa laa tahzan; wa qatalta nafsan fanajjainaaka minal ghammi wa fatannaaka futoonaa; falabista sineena feee ahli Madyana summa ji'ta 'alaa qadariny yaa Moosa
  20,41,Wastana' tuka linafsee
  20,42,Izhab anta wa akhooka bi Aayaatee wa laa taniyaa fee zikree
  20,43,Izhabaaa ilaa Fir'awna innahoo taghaa
  20,44,Faqoolaa lahoo qawlal laiyinal la allahoo yatazakkkaru 'aw yakhshaa
  20,45,Qaalaa Rabbanaaa innanaa nakhaafu ai yafruta 'alainaaa aw ai yatghaa
  20,46,Qaala laa takhaafaaa innanee ma'akumaa asma'u wa araa
  20,47,Faatiyaahu faqoolaaa innaa Rasoolaa Rabbika fa arsil ma'anaa Banee Israaa'eela wa laa tu'azzibhum qad ji'naaka bi Aayatim mir Rabbika wassa laamu 'alaa manit taba'al hudaa
  20,48,Innaa qad oohiya ilainaaa annnal 'azaaba 'alaa man kaz zaba wa tawalla
  20,49,Qaala famar Rabbu kumaa yaa Moosa
  20,50,Qaala Rabbunal lazeee a'taa kulla shai'in khalqahoo summa hadaa
  20,51,Qaala famaa baalul quroonil oolaa
  20,52,"Qaala 'ilmuhaa 'inda Rabee fee kitaab, laa yadillu Rabbee wa laa yansaa"
  20,53,Allazee ja'ala lakumul arda mahdanw wa salaka lakum feehaa subulanw wa anzala minas samaaa'i maaa'an fa akhrajnaa biheee azwaajam min nabaatin shatta
  20,54,Kuloo war'aw an'aamakum; inna fee zaalika la Aayaatil li ulin nuhaa
  20,55,Minhaa khalaqnaakum wa feehaa nu'eedukum wa minhaa nukhrijukum taaratan ukhraa
  20,56,Wa laqad arainaahu Aayaatinaa kullahaa fakaz zaba wa abaa
  20,57,Qaala aji'tanaa litukhri janaa min ardinaa bisihrika yaa Moosa
  20,58,Falanaatiyannaka bisihrim mislihee faj'al bainanaa wa bainaka maw'idal laa nukhlifuhoo nahnu wa laaa anta makaanan suwaa
  20,59,Qaala maw'idukum yawmuz zeenati wa ai yuhsharan naasu duhaa
  20,60,Fatawallaa Fir'awnu fajjama'a kaidahoo summa ataa
  20,61,"Qaala lahum Moosaa wailakum laa taftaroo 'alal laahi kaziban fa yus hitakum bi 'azaab, wa qad khaaba manif taraa"
  20,62,Fatanaaza'ooo amrahum bainahum wa asarrun najwaa
  20,63,Qaalooo in haaazaani lasaahiraani yureedaani ai yukhrijaakum min ardikum bisihrihimaa wa yazhabaa bitareeqatikumul muslaa
  20,64,Fa ajmi'oo kaidakum summma'too saffaa; wa qad aflahal yawma manis ta'laa
  20,65,Qaaloo yaa Moosaaa immaaa an tulqiya wa immaaa an nakoona awala man alqaa
  20,66,Qaala bal alqoo fa izaa hibaaluhum wa 'isiyyuhum yuhaiyalu ilaihi min sihrihim annahaa tas'aa
  20,67,Fa awjasa fee nafsihee kheefatam Moosa
  20,68,Qulnaa laa takhaf innaka antal a'laa
  20,69,Qa alqi maa fee yamee nika talqaf maa sana'oo; innamaa sana'oo kaidu saahir; wa laa yuflihus saahiru haisu ataa
  20,70,Fa ulqiyas saharatu sujjadan qaalooo aamannaa bi Rabbi Haaroona wa Moosa
  20,71,Qaala aamantum lahoo qabla an aazana lakum; innahoo lakabeerukumul lazee 'allama kumus sihra fala uqatti'anna aidiyakum wa arjulakum min khilaafinw wa la usallibannakum fee juzoo'in nakhli wa lata'lamunna aiyunaaa ashaddu 'azaabanw wa abqaa
  20,72,Qaaloo lan nu'siraka 'alaa maa jaaa'anaa minal baiyinaati wallazee fataranaa faqdi maaa anta qaad; innamaa taqdee haazihil hayaatad dunyaa
  20,73,Innaaa aamannaa bi Rabbinaa liyaghfira lanaa khataayaanaa wa maaa akrahtanaa 'alaihi minas sihr; wallaahu khairunw waabqaa
  20,74,Innahoo mai yaati Rabbahoo mujriman fa inna lahoo Jahannama laa yamotu feehaa wa laa yahyaa
  20,75,Wa mai yaatihee mu'minan qad 'amilas saalihaati fa ulaaa'ika lahumud dara jaatul 'ulaa
  20,76,Jannaatu 'Adnin tajree min tahtihal anhaaru khaalideena feehaa; wa zaalika jazaaa'ua man tazakka (section 3)
  20,77,Wa laqad awhainaaa ilaa Moosaaa an asri bi'ibaadee fadrib lahum tareeqan fil bahri yabasal laa takhaafu darakanw wa laa takhshaa
  20,78,Fa atba'ahum Fir'awnu bijunoodihee faghashiyahum minal yammmi maa ghashi yahum
  20,79,wa adalla fir'awnu qawmahoo wa maa hadaa
  20,80,Yaa Baneee Israaa'eela qad anjainaakum min 'aduw wikum wa wa'adnaakum jaanibat Tooril aimana wa nazzalnaa 'alaikumul Manna was Salwaa
  20,81,Kuloo min taiyibaati maa razaqnaakum wa laa tatghaw feehi fa yahilla 'alaikum ghadabee wa mai yahlil 'alaihi ghadabee faqad hawaa
  20,82,Wa innee la Ghaffaarul liman taaba wa aamana wa 'amila saalihan summah tadaa
  20,83,Wa maaa a'jalaka 'an qawmika yaa Moosa
  20,84,Qaala hum ulaaa'i 'alaaa asaree wa 'ajiltu ilaika Rabbi litardaa
  20,85,Qaala fa innaa qad fatannaa qawmaka mim ba'dika wa adallahumus Saamiriyy
  20,86,Faraja's Moosaaa ilaa qawmihee ghadbaana asifaa; qaala yaa qawmi alam ya'idkum Rabbukum wa'dan hasanaa; afataala 'alaikumul 'ahdu am arattum ai yahilla 'alaikum ghadabum mir Rabbikum fa akhlaftum maw'idee
  20,87,Qaaloo maaa akhlafnaa maw'idaka bimalkinna wa laakinna hummilnaaa awzaaram min zeenatil qawmi faqazafnaahaa fakazaalika alqas Saamiriyy
  20,88,Fa akhraja lahum 'ijlan jasadal lahoo khuwaarun faqaaloo haazaaa ilaahukum wa ilaahu Moosaa fanasee
  20,89,Afalaa yarawna allaa yarji'u ilaihim qawlanw wa laa yamliku lahum darranw wa laa naf'aa (section 4)
  20,90,Wa laqad qaala lahum Haaroonu min qablu yaa qawmi innamaa futintum bihee wa inna Rabbakumur Rahmaanu fattabi'oonee wa atee'ooo amree
  20,91,Qaaloo lan nabraha 'alaihi 'aakifeena hattaa yarji'a ilainaa Moosaa
  20,92,Qaala Yaa Haaroonu maa mana 'aka iz ra aitahum dallooo
  20,93,Allaa tattabi'ani afa'asaita amree
  20,94,Qaala yabna'umma laa taakhuz bilihyatee wa laa biraasee innee khashetu an taqoola farraqta baina Baneee Israaa'eela wa lam tarqub qawlee
  20,95,Qaala famaa khatbuka yaa Saamiriyy
  20,96,Qaala basurtu bimaa lam yabsuroo bihee faqabadtu qabdatam min asarir Rasooli fanabaztuhaa wa kazaalika sawwalat lee nafsee
  20,97,Qaala fazhab fa inna laka fil hayaati an taqoola laa misaasa wa inna laka maw'idal lan tukhlafahoo wanzur ilaaa ilaahikal lazee zalta 'alaihi 'aakifaa; lanuharriqannnahoo summa lanansifanahoo fil yammi nasfaa
  20,98,Innamaaa ilaahukkumul laahul lazee laa ilaaha illaa Hoo; wasi'a kulla shai'in ilmaa
  20,99,Kazaalika naqussu 'alaika min ambaaa'i maa qad sabaq; wa qad aatainaaka mil ladunnaa Zikraa
  20,100,"Man a'rada 'anhu, fa innahoo yahmilu Yawmal Qiyaamati wizraa"
  20,101,Khaalideena feehi wa saaa'a lahum Yawmal Qiyaamati himlaa
  20,102,Yawma yunfakhu fissoori wa nahshurul mujrimeena Yawma 'izin zurqaa
  20,103,Yatakhaafatoona bainahum il labistum illaa 'ashraa
  20,104,nahnu a'lamu bimaa yaqooloona iz yaqoolu amsaluhum tareeqatan illabistum illaa yawmaa (section 5)
  20,105,Wa yas'aloonaka 'anil jibaali faqul yansifuhaa Rabbee nasfaa
  20,106,Fa yazaruhaa qaa'an safsafaa
  20,107,Laa taraa feehaa 'iwajanw wa laaa amtaa
  20,108,Yawma iziny yattabi'oonad daa'iya laa 'iwaja lahoo wa khasha'atil aswaatu lir Rahmaani falaa tasma'u illaa hamsaa
  20,109,Yawma 'izil laa tanfa'ush shafaa'atu illaa man azina lahur Rahmaanu wa radiya lahoo qawlaa
  20,110,Ya'lamu maa bainaa aideehim wa maa khalfahum wa laa yauheetoona bihee 'ilmaa
  20,111,Wa 'anatil wujoohu lil Haiiyil Qaiyoomi wa qad khaaba man hamala zulmaa
  20,112,Wa mai ya'mal minas saalihaati wa huwa mu'minun falaa yakhaafu zulmanw wa laa hadmaa
  20,113,Wa kazaalika anzalnaahu Qur-aanan 'Arabiyyanw wa sarrafnaa fee hi minal wa'eedi la'allahum yattaqoona aw yuhdisu lahum zikraa
  20,114,Fata'aalal laahul Malikul Haqq; wa laa ta'jal bil Quraani min qabli ai yuqdaaa ilaika wahyuhoo wa qur Rabbi zidnee 'ilmaa
  20,115,Wa laqad 'ahidnaaa ilaaa Aadama min qablu fanasiya wa lam najid lahoo 'azmaa (section 6)
  20,116,Wa iz qulnaa lilma laaa'ikatis judoo li Aadama fasajadooo illaaa Iblees; abaa
  20,117,Faqulnaa yaaa Aadamu inna haazaa 'aduwwul laka wa lizawjika falaa yukhrijan nakumaa minal Jannati fatashqaa
  20,118,Innaa laka allaa tajoo'a feeha wa laa ta'raa
  20,119,Wa annaka laa tazma'u feehaa wa laa tadhaa
  20,120,Fa waswasa ilaihish Shaitaanu qaala yaaa Aadamu hal adulluka 'alaa shajaratil khuldi wa mulkil laa yablaa
  20,121,Fa akalaa minhaa fabadat lahumaa saw aatuhumaa wa tafiqaa yakhsifaani 'alaihimaa minw waraqil jannah; wa 'asaaa Aadamu Rabbahoo faghawaa
  20,122,Summaj tabbahu Rabbuhoo fataaba 'alaihi wa hadaa
  20,123,Qaalah bita minhaa jamee'am ba'dukum liba'din 'aduww; fa immaa yaati yannakum minnee hudan famanit taba'a hudaaya falaa yadillu wa laa yashhqaa
  20,124,Wa man a'rada 'an Zikree fa inna lahoo ma'eeshatan dankanw wa nahshuruhoo Yawmal Qiyaamati a'maa
  20,125,Qaala Rabbi lima hashar tanee a'maa wa qad kuntu baseeraa
  20,126,Qaala kazaalika atatka Aayaatunaa fanaseetahaa wa kazaalikal Yawma tunsaa
  20,127,Wa kazaalika najzee man asrafa wa lam yu'mim bi Aayaati Rabbih; wa la'azaabul Aakhirati ashaddu wa abqaa
  20,128,Afalam yahdi lahum kam ahlaknaa qablahum minal qurooni yamshoona fee masaakinihim; inna fee zaalika la Aayaatil li ulinnuhaa (section 7)
  20,129,Wa law laa Kalimatun sabaqat mir Rabbika lakaana lizaamanw wa ajalum musammaa
  20,130,Fasbir 'alaa maa yaqooloona wa sabbih bihamdi Rabbika qabla tuloo'ish shamsi wa qabla ghuroobihaa wa min aanaaa'il laili fasbbih wa atraafan nahaari la 'allaka tardaa
  20,131,Wa laa tamuddanna 'ainaika ilaa ma matta'na biheee azwajam minhum zahratal hayaatid dunya linaftinahum feeh; wa rizqu Rabbika khairunw wa abqaa
  20,132,Waamur ahlaka bis Salaati wastabir 'alaihaa la nas'aluka rizqaa; nahnu narzuquk; wal 'aaqibatu littaqwaa
  20,133,Wa qaaloo law laa yaateenaa bi Aayatim mmir Rabbih; awalam taatihim baiyinatu maa fis suhufil oolaa
  20,134,Wa law annaaa ahlaknaahum bi'azaabim min qablihee laqaaloo Rabbanaa law laaa arsalta ilainaa Rasoolan fanattabi's Aayaatika min qabli an nazilla wa nakhzaa
  20,135,Qul kullum mutarabbisun fatarabbasoo fasta'lamoona man Ashaabus Siraatis Sawiyyi wa manih tadaa (section 8)�(End Juz 16)
